name: Debug Symbols File
summary: Learn about .DBGSYM files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: DBGSYM files are used by programs such as Pidgin, a universal chat client that supports messaging services such as AIM, Google Talk, ICQ, and MSN.

description: Debugging file used by various Unix-based applications; stores debugging symbols used to report the status of the application and environment when a crash occurs; enables developers to trace bugs easier.
